      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 280,
        "height": 256,
        "content": "📊 WORKFLOW START\n\nThis workflow monitors Jira Epics and calculates health scores:\n\n• Runs every 6 hours\n• Fetches all Epics\n• Analyzes linked issues\n• Calculates health metrics\n• Flags at-risk epics\n• Updates dashboards\n• Alerts team via Slack"
